{"tid":265810,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 手切滷肉飯","createTime":"2017-06-01T03:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T11:04:15.000Z","uid":30742,"like":39,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed87678be2fe952b472c7b93e66873a2b1b8d67","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NWCoI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNWCoI.jpg&h=fc475e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O4dAu2ZdebM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO4dAu2ZdebM&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=be8b9e8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O4dAu2ZdebM</a><br />\n<br />\n上個月由花東返黎，一直都對台灣念念不忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n掛住架爛單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、掛住鹽水雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、掛住台灣早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （因為每日食得最豐富反而係早餐！）就算好辛苦&hellip;都好想再去&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣早餐台既滷肉飯間間都好好食的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n所以我又試下自己整<br />\n呢次我做手切的，唔同肉燥飯，呢個可以食到一粒粒豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得咁好食d～只係切既時間會累少少啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手切滷肉飯 圖文食譜:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/05/lu-rou-fan.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F05%2Flu-rou-fan.html&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7f5d883a\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/05/lu-rou-fan.html</a><br />\nFacebook :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d80f1892\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5bc8e2e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ad7757d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"350268530e7c9bdb3bb38bcc8d5718f54e13078d","tid":265810,"uid":16839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:15:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4683dbde92c46154188eb6f0bc7fae8a1ea896cf","tid":265810,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"蚊毛好快"},{"pid":"7d5f1da66dce78daa953a87992c021f67fe2a1ed","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:17:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蚊毛好快</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快鏡黎<br />\n<br />\n本身都係求求其其蚊走見到果d就算～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588f31fee1b696284a18deb01e11818574877a0f","tid":265810,"uid":27188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"如果唔落五香粉分別大唔大？"},{"pid":"c9a6fb136394e33a4022df0094a5bf0219047a77","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔落五香粉分別大唔大？</blockquote><br />\n會少左陣滷肉既香味！<br />\n<br />\n你唔介意都可以唔落既～不過幾蚊包～用少少～我都建議落番啦！<br />\n同埋好多其他野都有用到～唔會話用一次就放係度～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2314362c05e667c39878f9830afd524cc8a8c566","tid":265810,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"老娘整比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fa1e094d4f7874300dc3e846a57ebb7c5d6f8c","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘整比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a078a22f729f1461af88de5891a8e45b957a781","tid":265810,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e7d8b8901298a6840caca8c6452857f8e0b56e","tid":265810,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"有無腳切滷肉飯"},{"pid":"89afec9619f43a3001e40b385504b5871365b24b","tid":265810,"uid":23360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"4人份量？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成品好似好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41039e2c7ae0f6a570357893c1c7a6351ae1977","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無腳切滷肉飯</blockquote><br />\n你表演下～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82c50bf038ed06d72f3f0600f4ba15d3f0be3ce","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4人份量？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成品好似好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我通常一次會煮多d～慳電～<br />\n之後會食幾餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce75d9e6f548d96e59929b89ef437eea2956f445","tid":265810,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:10:42.000Z","msg":"老娘好勁，鍾意食嗰樣野可以自己煮返出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d78d48d67a2a97484138fd7231dabff3538bc84","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘好勁，鍾意食嗰樣野可以自己煮返出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔難～～<br />\n只要你好想好想食～但又好孤寒唔想比出面賺就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你想食咩？我識都可以煮～之後你跟住做你都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6d8c9f4dd8e94c74ee7bddd7f4971763f98d39","tid":265810,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:52:40.000Z","msg":"老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff7cc62b6241e90897cf8c1c7c51fae1a3c232c","tid":265810,"uid":23360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4人份量？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成品好似好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我通常一次會煮多d～慳電～<br />\n之後會食幾餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食唔哂點keep架？<br />\n你會點翻熱"},{"pid":"3f5b291b8eba4c2154439d8ec0cb9db67bf0609f","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4人份量？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成品好似好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我通常一次會煮多d～慳電～<br />\n之後會食幾餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食唔哂點keep架？<br />\n你會點翻熱</blockquote><br />\n幾日食得晒就放雪櫃下層，<br />\n幾唔晒就分開食唔晒果d入冰格（不過最好食晒佢啦！）<br />\n翻熱就咁煮番熱佢就ok架喇，唔洗落油落水，就咁一pat落pan煮熱就得架喇～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e8ed58c39e8d4afc6afb32fbe02d3567ff3397","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fc3a8c02ae6b11a19fa99f25f48b7679ffdb1a","tid":265810,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老娘好勁，鍾意食嗰樣野可以自己煮返出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔難～～<br />\n只要你好想好想食～但又好孤寒唔想比出面賺就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你想食咩？我識都可以煮～之後你跟住做你都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無咩菜色特別鍾意，好多野都食的，但我好鍾意食雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa38e175edf51852cf27eb116330865f609f4a5","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T10:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老娘好勁，鍾意食嗰樣野可以自己煮返出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔難～～<br />\n只要你好想好想食～但又好孤寒唔想比出面賺就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你想食咩？我識都可以煮～之後你跟住做你都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無咩菜色特別鍾意，好多野都食的，但我好鍾意食雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雞翼正呀！點整都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cd890e592f0b6f5d9676febfd848721934e741","tid":265810,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"老娘好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懶人唔願落廚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ec555d94b1e041732946e27fde0a6b5695c1c0","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懶人唔願落廚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為要食嘛...雙親唔係香港...煮得仲密<br />\n唔煮個妺你住家飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔懶得架...一懶就會唔想煮..就會生疏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c4839384c363f3f1414b01690574a1bee337ca","tid":265810,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老娘好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懶人唔願落廚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為要食嘛...雙親唔係香港...煮得仲密<br />\n唔煮個妺你住家飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔懶得架...一懶就會唔想煮..就會生疏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想日日自己煮<br />\n出街又污嘈又唔好食又唔值<br />\n不過又要買又要洗又要煮<br />\n然後又要洗<br />\n食唔哂聽日又食<br />\n平日要返工夜晚仲要玩你三粒鍾"},{"pid":"3d2432f03254b04fa3963f8839c9a83914168440","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老娘好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懶人唔願落廚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為要食嘛...雙親唔係香港...煮得仲密<br />\n唔煮個妺你住家飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔懶得架...一懶就會唔想煮..就會生疏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想日日自己煮<br />\n出街又污嘈又唔好食又唔值<br />\n不過又要買又要洗又要煮<br />\n然後又要洗<br />\n食唔哂聽日又食<br />\n平日要返工夜晚仲要玩你三粒鍾</blockquote><br />\n我放工都好難煮...<br />\n一係就煮快飯...即係蒸餸+菜或者焗肉+菜咁<br />\n或者假期慢煮左...放工一煎就起菜<br />\n要set死一個鐘就好煮好...<br />\n唔得我寧願唔煮<br />\n太夜食對身體都唔好...仲要無晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e86f14fd416688397d55d50e1feabc86933e3a5","tid":265810,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"睇相都覺得正，台灣正既魯肉飯就係咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934f1b0eed4aa8bf356271bda31f5c51fe270abc","tid":265810,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老娘整比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街"},{"pid":"4036efcd8390df8d47ba449012f9ae39c86efe97","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老娘整比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7da6b5d04f31e24346550db3f641208ccbed4b","tid":265810,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老娘整比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a088e66d02ad30ea66f77541a7071ed05684dd90","tid":265810,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老娘整比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6350cf05633c74fe094e55f034fb340746ba98ad","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇相都覺得正，台灣正既魯肉飯就係咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真正既滷肉飯一定要有皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cac1c60ef623caacf920b22ef6523df6c0dd23","tid":265810,"uid":25969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:51:21.000Z","msg":"呢個堅正，希望整得好食"},{"pid":"0e4e1d6c0b73658d2b97db32ed4f16ca5ed9542f","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個堅正，希望整得好食</blockquote><br />\n你會整？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1018ec353ddd319698879556eea1d21dc811fd63","tid":265810,"uid":25188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6871614483141c3299d5da96ea523ba6b46f4aa2","tid":265810,"uid":118710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66641e8f37ce3f880dfebd46af591c0e72e0ed6","tid":265810,"uid":12578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T18:46:15.000Z","msg":"買左幾多錢肉？四人份量？"},{"pid":"93f384eaacec1b1af652ac9384d96ea89663e788","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左幾多錢肉？四人份量？</blockquote><br />\n好似買左六十幾蚊～<br />\n<br />\n其實唔只～4個人每人兩碗啦～睇你大唔大食～<br />\n因為都燜得幾耐～為左用盡爐火～所以我會做多少少～留番之後食～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edca1196bccfe9592ca673a4fb4735208a085dd","tid":265810,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:13:06.000Z","msg":"老娘可唔可以下次整肉碎果隻肉燥飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 有無同你講我跟你個濕鍋雞煲食譜整 好食到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重落埋雞子 打邊爐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c7dfe762a5125aaa68a55ccf3e8fe3df535910","tid":265810,"uid":851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NWCoI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNWCoI.jpg&h=fc475e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O4dAu2ZdebM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO4dAu2ZdebM&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=be8b9e8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O4dAu2ZdebM</a><br />\n<br />\n上個月由花東返黎，一直都對台灣念念不忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n掛住架爛單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、掛住鹽水雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、掛住台灣早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （因為每日食得最豐富反而係早餐！）就算好辛苦&hellip;都好想再去&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣早餐台既滷肉飯間間都好好食的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n所以我又試下自己整<br />\n呢次我做手切的，唔同肉燥飯，呢個可以食到一粒粒豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得咁好食d～只係切既時間會累少少啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手切滷肉飯 圖文食譜:&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/05/lu-rou-fan.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F05%2Flu-rou-fan.html&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7f5d883a\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/05/lu-rou-fan.html</a><br />\nFacebook :&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d80f1892\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram:&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5bc8e2e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog:&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ad7757d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a></blockquote><br />\n又係老娘煮野食！我愛老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22145c68c45b6f1437cf9a256fcb38adac03d7e5","tid":265810,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘可唔可以下次整肉碎果隻肉燥飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 有無同你講我跟你個濕鍋雞煲食譜整 好食到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重落埋雞子 打邊爐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都可以呀！果個仲方便～但過一排先～因為食滷肉厭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 似唔似